SuperAdmin
==========

This crabgrass mod allow for god-like administration of all users
and groups in a particular site. 

Usage
=======

edit config/routes.rb
  map.from_plugin :super_admin

Specify the logins you want to be super_admins in sites.yml:

<begin>
default:
  name: crabgrass
  domain: localhost
  email_sender: 'crabgrass-system@localhost'
  secret: 'd24833cab5fafcd17f2c555f7663c0524a938e5ed6df2af8bf134d3959fc8ac3214fa8c7'
  pagination_size: 29
  super_admins:
  - sally
  - bob
<end>

restart rails and browse to: http://localhost:3000/admin


